","body":"아야 씨 덕분에 한 걸음 더 무사에 다가선 것 같아요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"band4-007-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"목표는 무사가 아니라 아이돌 아닙니까……!?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"band4-007-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"특훈인가~ 괜찮지 않아?\n나는 딱히 연습 안 해도 칠 수 있지만~ 뭐 심심하기도 하고!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"band4-007-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"저도 악기에 대한 지식이라면 약간 있습니다만……\n아이돌이 도대체 뭔지 잘 몰라서……\n아야 씨, 가르쳐 주십시오!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"band4-007-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":